==Trivia==
[[File:Vet'ion Chronicle art.png|thumb|200px|Vet'ion art from Jagex's turn-based card game ''[[rsw:Chronicle: RuneScape Legends|Chronicle: RuneScape Legends]]'']]
*Vet'ion's model is an enlarged, re-coloured version of [[Ranalph Devere]] from the [[Legends' Quest]].
*Vet'ion's examine is a reference to Tolkien's ''{{WP|The Return of the King}}''.
*Vet'ion's name is an anagram of {{RSL|Novite equipment|Novite}} from ''RuneScape''.
**Vet'ion's armour in his normal form matches the colour of Novite armour (tier 1) and the recolour in his reborn form matches {{RSL|Primal equipment|Primal armour}} (tier 99), both found within {{RSL|Daemonheim}} (located in the Wilderness).

